Project update process list
$Id$

Project home:
    http://sourceforge.net/projects/phpunixman

Chekc out cvs source code:
    export CVS_RSH=ssh 
    cvs -z3 -d:ext:chedong@cvs.sourceforge.net:/cvsroot/phpunixman co -P phpMan


Upload new release file to file release system
    ftp upload.sourceforge.net
    cd incoming
    put phpMan.php.gz

Update homepage:
    scp phpMan.php chedong@web.sourceforge.net:/home/groups/p/ph/phpunixman/htdocs/index.php


